::Zardus/DeathStorm::

Zardus picks up Tritan's distress signal. He looks down at his wrist. It was 
an alliance member. He puts his comm-link to his mouth. "DeathStorm, can you 
go to the new bot's coordinates and help him?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Off in the forest, DeathStorm nods. "On my way."

He looks at the coordinates that Zardus had transmitted to him. They were 
almost right next to him. In several minutes, he lands near the two new 
alliance members.

"Welcome. My name is DeathStorm."
